data.description: Welcome home. Discover modern comfort in this recently updated gem! The new LVP flooring & tasteful paint palette instill an atmosphere of warmth & comfort. Enjoy a spacious kitchen with stainless steel appliances and generous counter space making every meal a breeze to create, whether you're an aspiring home cook or a seasoned pro. Enjoy your favorite morning beverage with the spacious coffee bar. All this charm is nestled on a spacious corner lot just outside of Historic South Norfolk. Conveniently located near major highways for easy access to shopping, dining, & several military bases ensures you’re never far from where you want to be. Your dream home awaits!
